{"title":"这里有一扇窗——写在张志新的故乡","authors":["王干之"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":11,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里有一扇窗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——写在张志新的故乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王干之"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在黄家花园街上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一扇窗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它象人类的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把历史觑望："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它看见了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真正的历史悲剧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个共产党员呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被残杀在人民法场上！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在黄家花园街上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一扇窗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暗无天日的时刻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它会发光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵琴声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刺穿国民党达官显贵的心；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声声呐喊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫反动派魂飞魄丧……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在黄家花园街上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一扇窗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个勇敢的战士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从这里起步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把真理的钻石磨得发亮！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有民主和法制，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪有生机勃勃的景象？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在黄家花园街上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一扇窗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们祝愿它永远发光闪亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让它烛照"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史的行程，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让它暴露"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切反动魍魉……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}